`phackmud` `tQuest Board`

This utility helps you get on your feet by providing rewards for completing in-game quests and objectives!

Simply run: quest.run {name: "quest_name", s: #s.script.name, args: {}} when you want to complete a quest.
This allows us to monitor your progress and reward you once it's been complete!
`pHint` When a script asks you to pass an argument, add it to `Nargs` instead
